<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About BookLantern</h1>
    <p>
      <span class="highlight">BookLantern</span> is your free gateway to a world of knowledge and stories. Our platform is built to connect readers and learners with an expansive archive of books and documentaries — all at zero cost.
    </p>
    <p>
      We believe that access to information and culture should not come with barriers. BookLantern fetches open-access books from reliable online sources like Archive.org and other public libraries and presents them through a modern, stylized interface.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you’re here to explore timeless classics, academic materials, or simply dive into documentaries through our Watch page — BookLantern is here to support your curiosity.
    </p>
    <p>
      Join us by creating a free account, save your favorite books, track your reading, and enjoy new educational content added regularly by our team.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Your lantern to the world of knowledge starts here.</strong>
    </p>
  </div>
